headline: Why Are EMCOR (EME) Shares Soaring Today
summary: Shares of specialty construction contractor company EMCOR (NYSE:EME) jumped 8.7% in the afternoon session after an analyst at UBS raised the company's price target ahead of its upcoming earnings report.
